org.slc.sli.dashboard.client
Interface APIClient

All Known Implementing Classes:
SDKAPIClient
public interface APIClient

The application SDK interface to the SLI API. This is meant to be a thin wrapper around API calls. It groups together multiple API calls in some cases, hopefully in a way useful to the rest of the application.
